Package: soryos-system-lock
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: SoryOS Team <maintainers@soryos.local>
Depends: soryos-archive-keyring
Description: SoryOS APT system stability lock
 This package installs SoryOS APT pinning and stability helper commands.
 It protects SoryOS packages from replacement by other repositories while
 keeping Pop!_OS and Ubuntu available as low-priority fallback sources.
